There is an internal interface that we failed to implement on CodeParameter that looks like so:

``` C#
internal enum PARAMETER_PASSING_MODE
{
    cmParameterTypeIn = 1,
    cmParameterTypeOut = 2,
    cmParameterTypeInOut = 3
}

[ComImport()]
